      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To call this function you must pass a triplet of color space, transform type, and rendering intent for each color space in the chain of conversions. For example, the following code is equivalent to calling ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/2113677-cgcolorconversioninfocreate",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ":",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "// convert from `src` to `dst` space with default intent",
            "CGColorConversionInfoCreateFromList(NULL,",
            "    src, kCGColorConversionTransformFromSpace, kCGRenderingIntentDefault,",
            "    dst, kCGColorConversionTransformToSpace,   kCGRenderingIntentDefault,",
            "    NULL);"
          ],
          "metadata": {
            "anchor": "2754301",
            "title": "Listing 1"
          },
          "syntax": "occ",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To extend this example to convert through an intermediate color space, insert another space/type/intent triplet between the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "src",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "dst",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " lines, using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/coregraphics/cgcolorconversioninfotransformtype/kcgcolorconversiontransformapplyspace",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " type.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The listed color spaces must be calibrated color spaces (that is, not device-specific or indexed color spaces), and the list must contain at least two color spaces (that is, two triplets of space, type, and intent).",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can use a color conversion object to create ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/metalperformanceshaders/mpsimageconversion",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " filters that perform GPU-accelerated color space conversion. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
